304
00:18:04,920 --> 00:18:06,100
than Lou Mingye?

305
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,690
Of course.

306
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,560
When you lie,

307
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,930
