308
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:14,260
so that people can believe you.

309
00:18:15,790 --> 00:18:16,810
Okay then.

310
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:20,410
You really cared about
Lou Mingye before,

311
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:21,740
