320
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,420
How's that possible?

321
00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:48,260
I mean...

322
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:49,780
he's hard

323
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:51,140
