328
00:19:10,870 --> 00:19:11,710
Your Highness,

329
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:14,140
Feng Qing never got his hands dirty,

330
00:19:14,700 --> 00:19:15,980
and the murderer Huang Gui

331
00:19:15,980 --> 00:19:17,660
was killed halfway.

332
00:19:18,460 --> 00:19:19,820
Therefore, I've decided

333
00:19:20,370 --> 00:19:21,380
to release him.

334
00:19:22,500 --> 00:19:24,380
What a great file.

335
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,020
You managed to exonerate him.

336
00:19:27,780 --> 00:19:29,620
That's impressive.

337
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:31,980
I'm flattered.

338
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,340
It's just

339
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:35,100
a statement of fact.

340
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:38,100
The Huangs have got what they deserve.

341
00:19:38,380 --> 00:19:40,100
Just do what you want.

342
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:42,660
Mingye.

343
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,540
Actually,

344
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:50,260
I'm here for your servant Lan Che.

345
00:19:51,010 --> 00:19:52,060
Lan Che?

346
00:19:55,820 --> 00:19:56,660
Your Highness,

347
00:19:56,940 --> 00:19:58,300
Lan Che is straightforward.

348
00:19:58,420 --> 00:19:59,620
If she offends you...

349
00:19:59,620 --> 00:20:00,460
Oh, no.

350
00:20:00,700 --> 00:20:01,780
You got me wrong.

351
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,060
She's a good girl.

352
00:20:04,180 --> 00:20:06,240
She came from a common family,

353
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,830
but Mo and she really like each other.

354
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,580
It's all that matters

355
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:13,780
to a marriage.

356
00:20:15,170 --> 00:20:16,380
Your Highness, what?

357
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:20,140
But after all, Li Mo is my son.

358
00:20:20,980 --> 00:20:22,820
No matter how open-minded we are,

359
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:25,340
a servant and a princess

360
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:27,100
are not a match.

361
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:28,780
After all, we have to

362
00:20:28,780 --> 00:20:30,500
defend our reputation.

363
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:33,140
I know Lan Che is very capable.

364
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:35,380
How about this?

365
00:20:35,980 --> 00:20:37,420
How much is her indenture worth?

366
00:20:38,140 --> 00:20:39,500
I'll pay three times the price

367
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:40,540
for her.

368
00:20:41,700 --> 00:20:43,020
Your Highness, do you mean

369
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:46,180
Li Mo is going to marry her?

370
00:20:46,660 --> 00:20:47,500
Yes.

371
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:49,900
They're both adults.

372
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:50,940
It's pretty normal.

373
00:20:53,100 --> 00:20:54,060
Does Lan Che

374
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:56,500
know about this?

375
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,300
Don't worry.

376
00:20:58,790 --> 00:21:00,740
Unruly as he is,

377
00:21:00,740 --> 00:21:02,780
he'll never force her to marry him.

378
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:06,500
Just think about it.

379
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:13,940
What are you talking about?

380
00:21:15,820 --> 00:21:17,060
In this world,

381
00:21:17,740 --> 00:21:19,620
there are only two people
that I care about

382
00:21:19,620 --> 00:21:20,540
the most.

383
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:22,740
One is my father.

384
00:21:24,700 --> 00:21:25,740
The other one is you.

385
00:21:27,700 --> 00:21:28,900
Lan Che, I like you.

386
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:31,180
I've fallen in love with you

387
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:32,380
since I met you at Yuyan Tower.

388
00:21:45,820 --> 00:21:47,340
I'm a lazy

389
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:48,860
and careless person,

390
00:21:49,700 --> 00:21:50,780
but falling in love with you

391
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:53,540
is the most serious thing in my life.

392
00:21:55,740 --> 00:21:56,580
I...

393
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:58,260
I...

394
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:01,580
I've treated you like a good friend.

395
00:22:02,380 --> 00:22:05,260
I never thought you'd be

396
00:22:05,260 --> 00:22:06,500
my husband.

397
00:22:06,980 --> 00:22:08,220
Think about it now.

398
00:22:09,000 --> 00:22:11,420
What's so good about marriage?

399
00:22:12,380 --> 00:22:14,220
Cooking, doing laundry,
and raising kids,

400
00:22:14,580 --> 00:22:16,460
