in my family.

403
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,980
You do need to do these things.

404
00:22:23,980 --> 00:22:24,900
No.

405
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:27,420
Why don't you understand?

406
00:22:28,340 --> 00:22:29,620
Anyway, I won't marry you.

407
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:36,620
How about Lou Mingye?

408
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,300
Will you marry him?

409
00:22:48,860 --> 00:22:49,900
Li Mo,

410
00:22:50,180 --> 00:22:51,140
you will

411
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:53,340
find the love of your life.

412
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:56,140
I've been absent all afternoon.

413
00:22:56,340 --> 00:22:57,420
Goodbye.

414
00:23:00,780 --> 00:23:01,620
Lan Che,

415
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:03,140
I won't give up.

416
00:23:03,420 --> 00:23:04,740
I'll prove you

417
00:23:04,740 --> 00:23:06,100
I'm as good as Lou Mingye.

418
00:23:08,060 --> 00:23:11,140
(Lou's Mansion)

419
00:23:18,830 --> 00:23:19,670
My Lord.

420
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:26,260
Where were you this afternoon?

421
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:28,340
I...

422
00:23:29,740 --> 00:23:31,020
This afternoon...

423
00:23:32,140 --> 00:23:33,100
I...

424
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:34,420
did my friend a favor.

425
00:23:36,620 --> 00:23:37,460
My Lord,

426
00:23:37,460 --> 00:23:38,540
have some tea.

427
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:44,540
Is there anything you want to tell me?

428
00:23:48,060 --> 00:23:49,180
What?

429
00:23:57,340 --> 00:23:58,180
Lan Che,

430
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,180
how long have you worked here?

431
00:24:01,220 --> 00:24:02,260
Almost half a year.

432
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,900
Four months and ten days.

433
00:24:08,660 --> 00:24:09,780
I didn't expect you

434
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:12,220
to remember it so clearly.

435
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:16,100
If you find a better place,

436
00:24:17,740 --> 00:24:18,860
I won't force you to stay.

437
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:45,180
Who are you?

438
00:24:49,020 --> 00:24:49,860
Don't move,

439
00:24:49,980 --> 00:24:51,140
or I'll kill him!

440
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:15,460
My Lord.

441
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:19,300
What does that mean?

442
00:25:20,740 --> 00:25:21,580
My Lord!

443
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:24,940
Tuo Jiduo is dead.

444
00:25:26,900 --> 00:25:27,740
What?

445
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:34,300
My Lord.

446
00:25:34,820 --> 00:25:35,660
General.

447
00:25:35,860 --> 00:25:37,060
This person

448
00:25:37,060 --> 00:25:38,100
killed Tuo Jiduo.

449
00:25:39,380 --> 00:25:40,580
Tuo Jiduo is suspected of

450
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:42,260
assassinating the former
governor of Liangzhou.

451
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:43,860
This case is still unsolved,

452
00:25:43,860 --> 00:25:45,820
