453
00:25:46,260 --> 00:25:48,140
Now you've killed him.

454
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:51,020
Can you be responsible?

455
00:25:53,340 --> 00:25:55,340
Tuo Jiduo tried to escape

456
00:25:55,340 --> 00:25:57,260
and hijacked a jailer.

457
00:25:57,420 --> 00:25:58,540
I had no choice

458
00:25:58,540 --> 00:25:59,940
at that point.

459
00:26:00,100 --> 00:26:01,100
Please investigate it.

460
00:26:01,900 --> 00:26:02,740
Tell me,

461
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:04,740
why did you say Tuo Jiduo

462
00:26:04,740 --> 00:26:05,820
