463
00:26:06,860 --> 00:26:07,700
General,

464
00:26:08,020 --> 00:26:09,340
it's complicated.

465
00:26:09,660 --> 00:26:11,540
Someone pretended to deliver food

466
00:26:11,540 --> 00:26:12,620
and sneaked in

467
00:26:13,020 --> 00:26:14,260
to assassinate Tuo Jiduo.

468
00:26:14,460 --> 00:26:15,300
However,

469
00:26:15,300 --> 00:26:16,210
she failed

470
00:26:16,220 --> 00:26:17,820
