471
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:21,300
Take him down.

472
00:26:21,660 --> 00:26:22,500
Summon the assassin.

473
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:23,540
Aye.

474
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:24,820
Go!

475
00:26:45,840 --> 00:26:46,700
Huali?

476
00:26:47,860 --> 00:26:48,700
Huali,

477
00:26:48,870 --> 00:26:50,420
why did you sneak in

478
00:26:50,420 --> 00:26:51,620
to kill Tuo Jiduo?

479
00:26:53,300 --> 00:26:54,820
To avenge my father.

480
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:58,220
Who's your father?

481
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:00,900
Leng Quji.

482
00:27:09,140 --> 00:27:10,100
Then you're...

483
00:27:13,180 --> 00:27:14,220
Leng Qingyao.

484
00:27:28,820 --> 00:27:30,460
Since you're Leng Qingyao,

485
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:33,780
