486
00:27:36,380 --> 00:27:37,500
Everyone believes

487
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:40,020
it was my father who killed General Lou.

488
00:27:40,620 --> 00:27:42,460
My family was destroyed
because of this,

489
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:44,820
