500
00:28:20,980 --> 00:28:22,340
Besides, she couldn't make it.

501
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:23,860
Let's forget it.

502
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:28,780
I agree.

503
00:28:31,140 --> 00:28:32,220
Excellent.

504
00:28:33,860 --> 00:28:34,700
Qingyao,

505
00:28:35,140 --> 00:28:37,020
